@startuml

participant SalePipeline
participant SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler
participant ICustomersRepository
participant SaleContext

SalePipeline -> SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler : HandleAsync(context)
activate SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler

SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler -> ICustomersRepository : SearchCustomerByNitAsync(CustomerNit)
activate ICustomersRepository
ICustomersRepository --> SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler : customer?
deactivate ICustomersRepository

alt customer encontrado
    SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler -> SaleContext : IsNewCustomer = false
    SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler -> SaleContext : CustomerEntity = existingCustomer
else cliente nuevo
    SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler -> SaleContext : IsNewCustomer = true
    SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler -> SaleContext : CustomerEntity = new Customer(nit, fullName)
end

SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler -> SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler : base.HandleAsync(context)
note right : delega al siguiente handler
deactivate SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler

@enduml
